data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful, spacious home with a pool!  Recent updates include fresh paint, new flooring, and lovely landscaping.  Open family room with vaulted ceilings and a wall of windows overlooking the backyard.  Formal dining, breakfast room, and kitchen island bar provide plenty of seating for entertaining guests.  Enjoy the outdoor oasis in the private backyard setting.  Conveniently located near shopping and dining.  Just a block away from Woodbridge Golf Club.  This home is move-in ready for a new family to enjoy!
